## What is kimabo
    Kindle
        x
        Manga
           x
           Book

kimabo will fetch all images from a directory and create ready to copy kindle books

## Setup
install boost and compile boost filesystem lib http://www.boost.org/
download CImg and put in include path http://cimg.sourceforge.net/
cmake .
make

## Usage
    $ kimabo "Series Name" myimages/base/directory

## Result
    kindle
        /Series Name 01
                     /00000.png
                     /00001.png
                     ...
        /Series Name 02
                     /00000.png
                     ...
        ...

